{"type": "article", "id": 28642, "title": "可以自由调节的木架", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162312KxMT86luFzaecjrB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你不喜欢在木制家具上看到太多用来固定的五金件，工作室 <a href=\"http://www.ammarkalo.com/\">KALO</a> 近日设计的木架 Multi-Tier Shelf 或许会让你眼前一亮。这款木架最大的特点在于它的一体化设计，四根木腿依靠顶部的黄铜钉可以轻松地进行折叠或者调整高度，省去了不少运输和组装时的麻烦。在穿过下面的搁板时，缺口处的皮革衬垫则会护住木腿防止它们往下滑落。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.ammarkalo.com/Multi-Tier-Shelf\">链接</a>了解木架的详细规格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162306xzvSqAITB1brJoN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162306AEhbr8lqyZiOIRJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021623076S4bQTyz3fr5D1j2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162307E9GqY8vfZkH4hNpQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}